      "content": "yo can u help me with a headline for my news app?? i got these snippets from the downtown protest thing and need something that captures the energy.\n\n- crowds gathering near the city hall plaza around 2pm\n- large group of demonstrators calling for police reform and civil rights protections\n- several police vehicles stationed at intersections\n- some reports of shouting and minor scuffles between attendees and officers\n- march moving toward the courthouse now\n- local businesses starting to board up windows in the area",
